{
  "stem": "3874.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I wound up in Chateau Montintin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now, Chateau Montintin was a old, old castle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And on the outskirts-- well, it was not outskirts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was really the middle of a forest in Limoges-- there were farms around and so forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was in the middle of a forest, though.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was an abandoned-- it hadn't been lived in for years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When we got there-- well, first of all, the trip to Limoges, itself, it was horrendous.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The trains were overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Some of us were on top of the train, some were inside the trains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I mean, people were hanging on to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Some of the older kids-- those who were 14, 15, and 16-- couldn't even get on the trains, but we had one old truck there that one of the people would take them and go down to Chateau Montintin by this old truck.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Some of the kids were riding bicycles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was-- it was just horrendous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But when we did get to Chateau Montintin--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Approximately, it was about five or six days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, it was-- it was quite a while, because the trains kept stopping.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- there were bombings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we got to stations where the station had been bombed out, and they had to change trains.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it-- it was just horrendous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the road, you saw the effects of the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You saw-- this is first time I'd seen dead people on the road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know-- it was-- the roads were just crowded with people, just trying to get anywhere, get out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- it was just a horrendous experience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, there was a shortage of food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was the first time we experienced hunger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we did get the Chateau Montintin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very-- like an old chateau.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
